{"tag":"section","attrib":{"id":"idbaa85d25-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa","identifier":"/us/usc/t42/s1397b"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"1397b"},"text":"§ 1397b.","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Allotments","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"subsection","attrib":{"id":"idbaa85d26-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa","identifier":"/us/usc/t42/s1397b/a"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"a"},"text":"(a)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Computation of amounts for jurisdictions of Puerto Rico, Guam, etc.","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"The allotment for any fiscal year to each of the jurisdictions of Puerto Rico, Guam, the Virgin Islands, and the Northern Mariana Islands shall be an amount which bears the same ratio to the amount specified in subsection (c) as the amount which was specified for allocation to the particular jurisdiction involved for the fiscal year 1981 under ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t42/s1397a/a/2/C"},"text":"section 1397a(a)(2)(C) of this title","children":[],"tail":" (as in effect prior to "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1981-08-13"},"text":"Aug. 13, 1981","children":[],"tail":") bore to $2,900,000,000. The allotment for fiscal year 1989 and each succeeding fiscal year to American Samoa shall be an amount which bears the same ratio to the amount allotted to the Northern Mariana Islands for that fiscal year as the population of American Samoa bears to the population of the Northern Mariana Islands determined on the basis of the most recent data available at the time such allotment is determined."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"subsection","attrib":{"id":"idbaa85d27-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa","identifier":"/us/usc/t42/s1397b/b"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"b"},"text":"(b)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Computation of amounts for each State other than jurisdictions of Puerto Rico, Guam, etc.","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"chapeau","attrib":{},"text":"The allotment for any fiscal year for each State other than the jurisdictions of Puerto Rico, Guam, the Virgin Islands, American Samoa, and the Northern Mariana Islands shall be an amount which bears the same ratio to—","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"idbaa85d28-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa","identifier":"/us/usc/t42/s1397b/b/1"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"1"},"text":"(1)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" the amount specified in subsection (c), reduced by","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"idbaa85d29-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa","identifier":"/us/usc/t42/s1397b/b/2"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"2"},"text":"(2)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" the total amount allotted to those jurisdictions for that fiscal year under subsection (a),","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n\n"},{"tag":"continuation","attrib":{},"text":"as the population of that State bears to the population of all the States (other than Puerto Rico, Guam, the Virgin Islands, American Samoa, and the Northern Mariana Islands) as determined by the Secretary (on the basis of the most recent data available from the Department of Commerce) and promulgated prior to the first day of the third month of the preceding fiscal year.","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"subsection","attrib":{"id":"idbaa85d2a-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa","identifier":"/us/usc/t42/s1397b/c"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"c"},"text":"(c)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Appropriations","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"chapeau","attrib":{},"text":"The amount specified for purposes of subsections (a) and (b) shall be—","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"idbaa85d2b-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa","identifier":"/us/usc/t42/s1397b/c/1"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"1"},"text":"(1)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" $2,400,000,000 for the fiscal year 1982;","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"idbaa85d2c-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa","identifier":"/us/usc/t42/s1397b/c/2"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"2"},"text":"(2)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" $2,450,000,000 for the fiscal year 1983;","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"idbaa85d2d-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa","identifier":"/us/usc/t42/s1397b/c/3"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"3"},"text":"(3)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" $2,700,000,000 for the fiscal years 1984, 1985, 1986, 1987, and 1989;","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"idbaa85d2e-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa","identifier":"/us/usc/t42/s1397b/c/4"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"4"},"text":"(4)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" $2,750,000,000 for the fiscal year 1988;","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"idbaa85d2f-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa","identifier":"/us/usc/t42/s1397b/c/5"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"5"},"text":"(5)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" $2,800,000,000 for each of the fiscal years 1990 through 1995;","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"idbaa85d30-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa","identifier":"/us/usc/t42/s1397b/c/6"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"6"},"text":"(6)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" $2,381,000,000 for the fiscal year 1996;","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"idbaa85d31-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa","identifier":"/us/usc/t42/s1397b/c/7"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"7"},"text":"(7)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" $2,380,000,000 for the fiscal year 1997;","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"idbaa85d32-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa","identifier":"/us/usc/t42/s1397b/c/8"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"8"},"text":"(8)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" $2,299,000,000 for the fiscal year 1998;","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"idbaa85d33-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa","identifier":"/us/usc/t42/s1397b/c/9"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"9"},"text":"(9)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" $2,380,000,000 for the fiscal year 1999;","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"idbaa85d34-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa","identifier":"/us/usc/t42/s1397b/c/10"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"10"},"text":"(10)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" $2,380,000,000 for the fiscal year 2000; and","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"idbaa85d35-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa","identifier":"/us/usc/t42/s1397b/c/11"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"11"},"text":"(11)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" $1,700,000,000 for the fiscal year 2001 and each fiscal year thereafter.","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"sourceCredit","attrib":{"id":"idbaa85d36-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa"},"text":"(","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us